The paper proposes a new measure for tracing the historical development of scientific knowledge in citation networks of scientific publications. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including social and information networks (cs.SI), digital libraries (cs.DL), cybernetics (cs.CY), systems and control (cs.SD), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
